item.title: About
item.description: I am a Gothenburg-based developer, with deep experience building and scaling distributed systems. When not at Forza Football getting done whatever needs getting done, I hack on open source projects, explore nature and learn new things. I write to remember and share my learnings. Move fast, take risks, release early, keep things simple and be a cheerful spirit.
